Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十八幕\N決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒因恐懼而逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧為軍人的兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身體只留下他的軀殼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人已不在這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾經思念的人已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我證明給您看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懸 總算趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給他寫了生日卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個年紀了又不好意思親手交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我走之後你再交給阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦率點自己給他不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 因為他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有義務保護那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請見諒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿爾貝先生向伯爵正式提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝…阿爾貝還只是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在那份上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生已有子爵身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場決鬥沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的孤獨…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…一切都由我來承擔吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫爾塞夫伯爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請仔細看著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是愛德蒙·唐泰斯已死的證據！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不叫我起來 弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正等著呢 這一刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為巖窟王便意味著不再是人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身的組織都變成結晶之時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心的溫度也不斷下降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終連心也會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從痛苦中解放出來的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心也沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒 悲傷 憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最害怕的就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最後留下的就是心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他作為人 如果還留有心之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只有心臟不會不滅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖窟王…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣…直衝我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就在此刻下勝利的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那卑鄙的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費爾南·蒙代戈和梅爾塞苔絲生下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受詛咒之子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沐浴在陽光中的你不會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無辜被奪去青春的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孤獨飢餓而倒下的老人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切因果輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒在此刻成為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨著你的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨著你的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被此劍貫穿吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上…醫生馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…睡得真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥…很有效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和你…練過劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的…決鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了…夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好意思…對我諸多要求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲 弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾…貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天…我做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去年吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是前年呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和歐仁妮三人一起…去了諾曼底對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…好像又是法國南部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人躺在沙灘上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你慶祝生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風很大…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬一口奶酪…都是沙子的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐仁妮那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的帽子被吹走…還鬧彆扭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy…Birthday…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十六歲…生日快樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲…再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上…醫生馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的…會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…很溫暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我獨自走在夜色昏沉中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十九幕\N即使我將不再是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待

